QuestData.Title: Naval Domination
QuestData.Description: Our naval domination continues!$b$bHowever, we are going to need even more experience and resources to take this shipyard to the next level. Once we reach our goals, we can upgrade the capacity of the shipyard to hold even more ships!
QuestData.LogDescription: Collect 2500 garrison resources, 2500 gold and complete 25 naval treasure missions.
